item.title: Mas Holdings
item.description: From Distributed Denial of Secrets RELEASE MAS Holdings 29 gigabytes of hacked files from MAS Holdings, South Asia’s largest manufacturer of lingerie and one of Sri Lanka’s largest apparel manufacturers. DATASET DETAILS COUNTRIES Sri Lanka TYPE Hack SOURCE Nefilim FILE SIZE 29 GB DOWNLOADS (How to Request Access) MORE REFERENCES EDITOR NOTES 29 gigabytes of hacked files from MAS Holdings, South Asia’s largest manufacturer of lingerie and one of Sri Lanka’s largest apparel manufacturers.
